# 🌐 Infrastructure Overview. (Agri-Tech + Solana)

This folder contains the technical blueprints and module-level implementations for our smart agriculture infrastructure, powered by Solana and deployed via Rust-based smart contracts.

## 🧱 Subdirectory Structure

```bash
infrastructure/
├── sensor_node/
│   ├── sensor_emitter.rs
│   ├── serial_bridge.rs
│   └── README.md
├── blockchain_gateway/
│   ├── solana_rpc_listener.rs
│   ├── transaction_broadcaster.rs
│   └── README.md
├── explorer_ui/
│   ├── data_dashboard_react/
│   ├── components/
│   ├── pages/
│   └── README.md
├── node_deployment/
│   ├── validator_config.yaml
│   ├── install_solana_node.sh
│   └── deployment_guide.md
├── iot_oracle/
│   ├── oracle_router.rs
│   ├── contract_feeder.rs
│   └── README.md
└── README.md
```
